				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10598142/scp-4808#post-4207214</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2019 07:46:53 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Basman777</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5225559</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I love this! Great 'what the hell?'-factor with just enough information to try to grasp at the bigger picture.</p> <p>Wasn't sure about the dead dog because up until that point I assumed there was some sort of benevolent force giving these people a second shot at a fulfilled life in the form of a dog. Thanks for educating me on what a shaggy dog joke is, it opened my eyes to the creativity of this SCP. Makes me wonder if the other suicide deaths were also followed by a dead instance of SCP-4808-1?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
