age:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2902864)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" >MaliceAforethought</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552231131" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" >DrChandra</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1345012&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552231131" alt="kinchtheknifeblade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1345012)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" >kinchtheknifeblade</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4894577&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552231131" alt="Laneous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4894577)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" >Laneous</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552231131" alt="FloppyPhoenix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" >FloppyPhoenix</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gishface" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2314483&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552231131" alt="gishface" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2314483)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gishface" >gishface</a></span> for critique.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;In&nbsp;case&nbsp;you&nbsp;don't&nbsp;get&nbsp;it...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;bork</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>These people live long, unfulfilling lives, punctuated by shaggy dogs. Shaggy dog jokes are long, unfulfilling jokes punctuated by shaggy dogs. The PoI finally figured out how to &quot;cut&quot; the joke short.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
